Summary: 
 * Merge from the following branches
 - SystemC-Examples--mainline--0.3
 - SystemC-Examples--mainline--0.4,
 - SystemC-Examples--da-deyhle--0.4

 * Fixed small bug in systemoc-fir example

 * Added --generate-problemgraph code to
   systemoc-sdf and systemoc-select examples

 * Fixed design-select.cpp to only declare its firing states
   as member variables

 * adapted sources of fir, sdf and sqr examples for easier synthesis
   replaced templates, added helper includefile to examples fir, sdf and sqr
   added syntesis rules to Makefiles of examples fir, sdf and sqr

 * adapted idct2d-test example for easier synthesis
   added smoc_synth_std_includes.hpp, adapted Makefile.am

 * adapted Makefiles of fir, sdf, sqr, idct for relative pathnames
 * adapted configure.in Makefile.am for relative pathname

 * bugfix in mpeg4 Makefile.am

 * Added comments for parser.hpp

 * extended timelogger to write additional callcount into logfile
 * removed unnecessary output
 * added logger for packet latencies
 * extended example to use logger of latencies

 * added missing script files
 * modified evaluation script to add simulation of example without vpc
 * corrected start script to tar NoVPC runs into correct archiv  * corrected start script to tar NoVPC runs into correct archive
 * modified rsmodule to only initialize once
 * added config ands stimulis to test

 * fixed doxygen warnings

 * Modified systemoc-mpeg4 design-test-idct2d.cpp example
 - NDEBUG, XILINX_EDK_RUNTIME, USE_COUNTER_INPUT
 - Miscellaneous beautifications
 - Deactivated cout for XILINX_EDK_RUNTIME
 - Removed comments, so that overall project compiles correctly

